text: Takeaki Tsuchiya (born 18 May 1970) is a Japanese equestrian. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Japan Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Miyazaki Prefecture
